    <item>
      <title>特朗普承诺不对加班税征税，争取蓝领选民投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/trump-pledges-no-taxes-on-overtime-in-pitch-to-blue-collar-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党人唐纳德·特朗普在辩论表现不佳几天后的一次集会上承诺取消加班税，这位总统候选人希望通过一项新的民粹主义减税方案翻开新的一页。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/trump-pledges-no-taxes-on-overtime-in-pitch-to-blue-collar-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 23:01:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>监管机构称中国在全球放贷规模超过美国数十亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/watchdog-details-china-s-dominance-over-us-in-global-lending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份政府监督报告显示，过去八年，中国在全球基础设施项目上的投入几乎是美国的九倍，这凸显了华盛顿在较贫穷国家与北京争夺影响力时面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/watchdog-details-china-s-dominance-over-us-in-global-lending</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 22:23:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工会“坚决”反对，称美国钢铁交易“注定失败”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/us-steel-deal-with-nippon-called-doomed-by-steelworkers-union</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国钢铁工人联合会表示，它不会被迫接受新日本制铁公司为收购美国钢铁公司而争取工人支持的最后一搏，称这笔价值 141 亿美元的收购是一笔“注定失败的交易”，并誓言要抵制任何外国对该公司所有权的收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/us-steel-deal-with-nippon-called-doomed-by-steelworkers-union</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 22:14:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在佐治亚州的刑事案件因部分指控被撤销而缩小范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/trump-criminal-case-in-georgia-narrowed-as-some-counts-tossed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，佐治亚州一名法官缩小了该州针对前总统试图推翻 2020 年大选结果的刑事案件范围，唐纳德·特朗普取得了法律胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/trump-criminal-case-in-georgia-narrowed-as-some-counts-tossed</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 21:28:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
